  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Turkish plane crashes at Katunayake airport",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "An A 330-300 Air Bus type plane that was about to depart for Turkey from Kattu Nayaka Airport on Sunday night has crashed.",
        "The cargo flight from Istanbul, Turkey, was about to depart the country with 45 metric tons of clothes on board, airport officials said.",
        "They said that the accident occurred when a container brought to the plane collided with the plane's engine due to prevailing strong winds.",
        "Due to this, the airport officials have said that there is a problem in leaving the country."
      ],
